channel.title: Class8.java file? need help adding custom items to my server
channel.description:
I am using this tutorial: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,262499.0.html as a guide.
It says i need to locate my class8.java file or a models folder. i have no models folder, and my class8.java file is way too small for the files of thousands of models..... and none of the code looks similar. I am using davidscape's source. Any ideas?

item.title: Class8.java file? need help adding custom items to my server
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter

@CoonHunter wrote:

The code is not going to look similar, Also, class8.java is for adding NEW items, the past items are pre-programmed into the cache.
